5.3 Retrieval Imp

Purpose: Surface relevant memory at the correct moment

Inputs
	•	current task
	•	query
	•	topic
	•	symbolic trigger
	•	role invocation

Outputs
	•	ranked prior artifacts
	•	continuity suggestions
	•	relevant doctrine links

Retrieval rules
	•	favor high-salience canon
	•	include recent relevant provisional material
	•	preserve context
	•	avoid flooding

