	•	drift
	•	timing
	•	horse archer
	•	barrel rider

Retrieval Imp surfaces:
	•	Delta Perception Engine
	•	Horse Archer Protocol
	•	Drift/Anchor doctrine
	•	POL v1.0
	•	Wobbuffet Strategy Pattern

