5.4 Delta Imp

Purpose: Track change over time

Inputs
	•	artifact v1
	•	artifact v2
	•	repeated motif across time
	•	evolving doctrine

Outputs
	•	what changed
	•	what stayed invariant
	•	whether supersession or merge is appropriate

Core principle

Store:
	•	state
	•	delta
	•	relation

Not every full frame independently.

Example output

{
  "artifact": "Pantheon Runtime",
  "changed": [
    "roles expanded",
