Mother Duck pass

Determines:
	•	Barrel Rider = provisional protocol
	•	Horse Archer = strategy doctrine candidate
	•	internal anchor = existing doctrine reinforcement
	•	drift surfing = merge into Drift Control module

Storage result
	•	one new provisional artifact
	•	one doctrine amendment
	•	one crosslink entry
	•	one archive note preventing duplication

