13. Why this architecture works

It solves four memory problems at once:

1. Clutter

Imps organize before accumulation becomes chaos

2. Drift

Mother Duck preserves invariant continuity

3. Retrieval failure

Retrieval Imp surfaces what matters when relevant

4. Reinvention

Crosslink + Delta Imps reduce repeated rediscovery

